<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٩٦ - وَسَأَلْنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرَ بْنَ عَبْدِ اللهِ </a>فَقَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَا يَقْرَبَنَّهَا حَتَّى يَطُوفَ بَيْنَ الصَّفَا وَالْمَرْوَةِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>